---
title: Supercharged Falafel Bowls with Hummus Dressing and Spiced Pita Crisps
description: This recipe proves that a few humble ingredients can come together to make an unforgettable dinner! Fresh veggies are the star of these wholesome bowls, supported by savoury pita chips and crispy falafels. It's a combo so delicious, you won't want to put your fork down.
